author: adrianc
msg: Internationalization note: this commit contains new UI labels.
Deprecated the time of day expression - it was a bad design. Replaced it with separate hour and minute expressions.
Fixed the createTemporalExpression service. It wouldn't allow user-specified expression IDs.

author: sf
msg: Turn static function get_server_name_for_url() into public function
ap_get_server_name_for_url() and use it where appropriate. This fixes
mod_rewrite generating invalid URLs for redirects to IPv6 literal addresses.
